(114, 3, '2018-10-11 17:51:08', '2018-10-11 14:51:08', 'pecify a single box-shadow using:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Two, three, or four <code><a href=\"http://docset.velocity/CSS.docset/developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/length.html\">&lt;length&gt;</a></code> values.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>If only two values are given, they are interpreted as <code><a href=\"http://docset.velocity/CSS.docset/developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/box-shadow.html?v=a#&lt;offset-x&gt; &lt;offset-y&gt;\">&lt;offset-x&gt;&lt;offset-y&gt;</a></code> values.</li>\r\n 	<li>If a third value is given, it is interpreted as a <code><a href=\"http://docset.velocity/CSS.docset/developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/box-shadow.html?v=a#&lt;blur-radius&gt;\">&lt;blur-radius&gt;</a></code>.</li>\r\n 	<li>If a fourth value is given, it is interpreted as a <code><a href=\"http://docset.velocity/CSS.docset/developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/box-shadow.html?v=a#&lt;spread-radius&gt;\">&lt;spread-radius&gt;</a></code>.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li>Optionally, the <code><a href=\"http://docset.velocity/CSS.docset/developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/box-shadow.html?v=a#inset\">inset</a></code> keyword.</li>\r\n 	<li>Optionally, a <code><a href=\"http://docset.velocity/CSS.docset/developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/box-shadow.html?v=a#&lt;color&gt;\">&lt;color&gt;</a></code> value.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'box-shadow syntax', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'box-shadow-syntax', '', '', '2018-10-15 11:39:44', '2018-10-15 08:39:44', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=114', 0, 'post', '', 0),
